# TargetMaps — Design System for Claude
# claude.design v1.0 · 2026-06-29
#
# DROP THIS FILE IN ANY REPO.
# Claude will apply TargetMaps brand identity when generating
# DOCX, PPTX, XLSX, HTML, or PDF documents.
#
# Source of truth: imagen_institucional_targetmaps/
# Scripts:         scripts/tm_brand.py · tm_docx.py · tm_pptx.py · tm_xlsx.py
# Templates:       templates_targetmaps/*.dotx · *.potx
# Logos CDN:       https://github.com/fhorna-lab/branding_targetmaps

