| blue_dark      | #273371 | (39, 51, 113)    | Dark backgrounds, cover, H1, callout bg    |
| blue_mid       | #2F71B8 | (47, 113, 184)   | H2, table header, bars, separators         |
| gray           | #909091 | (144, 144, 145)  | Secondary text, footnotes, footer          |
| table_stripe   | #F2F6FB | (242, 246, 251)  | Even table rows                            |
| table_border   | #C0C4CC | (192, 196, 204)  | Table grid borders (0.5pt)                 |
| bg_light       | #F2F2F2 | (242, 242, 242)  | Confidentiality block, neutral bg          |
| white          | #FFFFFF | (255, 255, 255)  | Page background, odd table rows            |
| black          | #000000 | (0, 0, 0)        | Body text                                  |
| subtotal       | #D5E2F4 | (213, 226, 244)  | Subtotal rows in Excel (between stripe/total) |
| geocoder       | #169A38 | (22, 154, 56)    | Product: GeoCoder                          |
| geoanalytics   | #28529F | (40, 82, 159)    | Product: GeoAnalytics                      |
