## LOGOS

Base URL: `https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fhorna-lab/branding_targetmaps/main/`

| Key          | URL / Path                                                 | Use                              |
|--------------|------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| color        | …/targetmaps_Logo.png                                      | White / light backgrounds        |
| white        | …/Original_logo_TargetMaps_Blanco.png                      | Dark backgrounds (#273371)       |
| white_alt    | …/logo_TargetMaps_Blanco.png                               | Dark backgrounds (alt)           |
| firma        | …/targetmaps_Logo_firma.png                                | With signature                   |
| small        | …/targetmaps_Logo_small.png                                | Compact spaces                   |
| sin_gab      | …/targetmaps_Logo_sin_GAB.png                              | Without "GEO ANALYTICS" tagline  |
| whatsapp     | …/targetmaps_Logo_whatsapp.png                             | Social media / WhatsApp          |
| geocoder     | …/targetmaps_GeoCoder.png                                  | Product: GeoCoder                |
| geoanalytics | …/targetmaps_GeoAnalitics.png                              | Product: GeoAnalytics            |
| leadgen      | …/targetmaps_LeadGenerator.png                             | Product: LeadGenerator           |
| navego       | …/logoNavego.png                                           | Product: Navego360               |

Logo rules:
- Light background → logo `color`
- Dark background (#273371) → logo `white`
- NEVER distort, rotate, recolor, or add shadows
- Minimum exclusion zone: `x` on all sides (ideally `2x`)
- Never duplicate logo in body if cover template already has it in the header

