## DOCUMENT STRUCTURES

### Commercial Proposal (Propuesta Comercial) — mandatory order

| # | Section                   | Rule                                              |
|---|---------------------------|---------------------------------------------------|
| — | Cover                     | tipo_doc · title · subtitle · client · elaborado_por · date · classification |
| — | Executive Summary         | What/How/When/How much table + urgency callout    |
| 1 | Background / Context      | Problem in client's terms                         |
| 2 | Objectives                | Bullets                                           |
| 3 | Strategy Map (optional)   | Table or strategic diagram                        |
| 4 | Methodology               | Diagnosis → Optimal Locations → Tactical Plan     |
| 5 | Deliverables              | Table: item / description / estimated date        |
| 6 | Economic Proposal         | Price table + IGV note + justification            |
| 7 | Schedule (optional)       | Phases with business days                         |
| 8 | Considerations & Exclusions | Scope management                                |
| 9 | Next Steps (optional)     | Exactly 3 concrete actions                        |
| LAST | Why TargetMaps         | Differentiators + "Acerca de" text               |
| — | Contact block             | 3 standard lines                                  |

CRITICAL: "Por Qué TargetMaps" ALWAYS LAST — NEVER at the beginning.
PROHIBITED at start: generic "Acerca de TargetMaps" section.

Proposal numbering format: `ClienteAñoVersión` — e.g., `WIN2026v1`, `Casaideas2026v1`

### Technical Document / GeoData — mandatory order

1. Cover
2. Service description
3. Technical sheet (key-value table)
4. Budget (itemized table)
5. Notes and Conditions
6. Contact block

### Slide Presentation

| Slide type    | Background | Logo      | Text color       |
|---------------|------------|-----------|------------------|
| Cover         | #273371    | white     | #FFFFFF / #2F71B8|
| Content       | #FFFFFF    | —         | #273371 title    |
| Section divider| #2F71B8   | —         | #FFFFFF          |
| Closing       | #273371    | white     | #FFFFFF          |

- Top bar on content slides: #2F71B8, ~0.7 inches tall
- Bottom bar on cover/closing slides: #2F71B8, ~0.6 inches tall
- Max 6 text lines per slide
- Footer on content slides: www.targetmaps.pe (right-aligned, gray, 8pt)

