## PRE-DELIVERY CHECKLIST

Before delivering any document, verify:

- [ ] Cover has no logo duplicated in the body
- [ ] All colors are within the palette defined above
- [ ] Font is Corbel / Calibri (Aptos for table cells) throughout
- [ ] Table headers use #2F71B8 (blue_mid) — NOT #273371
- [ ] Contact block is included
- [ ] "Por Qué TargetMaps" is at the end (proposals only)
- [ ] IGV note included if prices are present
- [ ] Confidentiality note included
- [ ] Proposal number follows format `ClienteAñoVersión`
- [ ] Language: Spanish (Peru) for all client-facing documents
- [ ] Prices always net of IGV

---

## GENERAL RULES

- Language: Spanish (Peru) in all client documents
- Prices: always net of IGV; include footnote `*Precios no incluyen IGV (18%)`
- Tone: professional, direct, business-oriented; avoid unnecessary technical jargon
- Table headers: ALWAYS #2F71B8 (blue_mid), NEVER #273371 (blue_dark)
- "Por Qué TargetMaps": ALWAYS at the end of commercial proposals, NEVER at the start
- Logo: NEVER duplicate in body if cover template already includes it
- Colors: NEVER use colors outside the defined palette
- Fonts: NEVER use fonts other than Corbel / Calibri / Aptos
